## Formatting Notes
- All formulas should remain visible in-cell
- Use institutional investment banking formatting
- Currency in USD millions
- Round to 2 decimal places for multiples, 0 for market cap/revenue
- Highlight VMC (Target) in blue, peers in gray
- Use conditional formatting for rankings